creator: iYaliSai ​இயலிசை
descriptionHtml:
iYaliSai RADIO is a Tamil online live streaming radio that breezes to your door with high quality Tamil Cinema and Hindu Bhakti songs in selected mode.

The new iYaliSai RADIO app gives you the best experience when it comes to listening to Tamil, English and Sinhala online radios and FM radios.

- Listen Tamil FM radios.
- Listen Sri Lanka FM radios.
- Listen Tamil Hindu Bhakti radios.
- Listen Tamil Catholic and Christian radios.
- Listen Tamil Muslim radio.
- Listen Sinhala FM radios.
- Listen English FM radios.

App Features,

- Lock screen control (play, pause, next radio)
- Categories : Choose your favourite radio station/s from different categories.
- My Faves : Easily access the stations you chose from different categories.
- My Theme : Select your favourite theme according to your mode.
- Sleep timer : Set a sleep timer to turn the app off automatically.
- Super cool interface and Fast loading

Some third party radios' streaming quality may vary from 48 kbps to 128 kbps MP3. Some of them are not 24/7 services.

iYaliSai RADIO app requires an internet connection (mobile data or Wi-Fi) in order to tune in radio stations and storage permission for favourite function.

Our website : https://www.iyalisai.com

Find iYaliSai RADIO on Social Networks,

https://facebook.com/iYaliSaiRadio
https://instagram.com/iYaliSaiRadio
https://youtube.com/user/iYaliSaiRadio

Listen to the audio you love and Enjoy listening 🎧.
